    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks for this initiative!\r\n\r\nI don't get the same size results for the Minified + GZipped bundle with [Bundlesize](https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize):\r\n\r\n- Before (Uglify): 63.24 KB\r\n- After (Closure): 65.06 KB\r\n\r\nThis would mean that Uglify leads to a better GZipped bundle.\r\n\r\nIs that something that you would have expected?",
